Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.89,0:00:11.90,Title,Title,0,0,0,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\fs16\alpha&H66&\an7\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H0075EA&}ACG12调查小队【沉默似金_】抄自【F宅字幕组】\N仅供学习交流，禁止用于任何商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.96,0:00:02.43,Default,Felt,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.43,0:00:04.01,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,菲鲁特 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.01,0:00:06.88,Default,Felt,0,0,0,,小哥 你够得到掉在这里面的百圆硬币吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.88,0:00:07.86,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,即视感？！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.89,0:00:11.90,Title,Title,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an2}{\1c&HA86C6F&}Re{\1c&HA9AB4B&}:{\1c&H7D60CC&}小{\1c&H4396E0&}剧场 {\1c&H000000&}其六
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.90,0:00:16.87,SignC,Title,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1500)\1c&H9A7CFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}小{\1c&H4FB4FF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}剧场{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HC4C700&\b1\bord6}⑥{\bord2}{\3c&HFFFFFF&\1c&HB8B80F&}不是{\1c&HBB878E&\3c&HFFFFFF&}猪的{\1c&HC2BA20&\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\1c&H9A7CFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}愿{\1c&H4FB4FF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.29,0:00:15.76,Default,Felt,0,0,0,,没时间做这种事了 和莱茵哈鲁特那家伙的...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.76,0:00:16.81,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,又来？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.81,0:00:19.75,Default,Felt,0,0,0,,我在和他比谁能先夹到大人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.75,0:00:21.87,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,果真是和和睦睦相亲相爱的剧本
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.87,0:00:23.16,Default,Felt,0,0,0,,烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.16,0:00:25.73,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,然后莱茵哈鲁特一个劲地夹到大人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.73,0:00:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,菲鲁特却一个都夹不到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.46,0:00:30.38,Default,Felt,0,0,0,,只能拿到这百圆硬币扭转局势了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.38,0:00:33.64,Default,Priscilla,0,0,0,,我听见了哪家丧家犬的呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.05,0:00:35.87,Default,Felt,0,0,0,,我现在很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.87,0:00:37.33,Default,Felt,0,0,0,,没空理你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.33,0:00:38.53,Default,Priscilla,0,0,0,,即便看到这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.53,0:00:39.47,Default,Felt,0,0,0,,那个是...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.74,0:00:43.56,Default,Priscilla,0,0,0,,交给妾身的话此等玩乐宛若儿戏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.89,0:00:45.39,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,真的假的 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.39,0:00:47.89,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,什么都能做到的人真的存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.89,0:00:50.99,Default,Priscilla,0,0,0,,虽然耳朵里面吹进了你们吵闹的胡话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.99,0:00:53.97,Default,Priscilla,0,0,0,,那边的凡人 你就如此拘泥于胜负吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.97,0:00:55.20,Default,Felt,0,0,0,,碍着你了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.20,0:00:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是无论如何都想赢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.12,0:00:58.66,Default,Priscilla,0,0,0,,无论如何 吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.66,0:01:02.32,Default,Felt,0,0,0,,对 无论如何都想得到这个人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.32,0:01:05.20,Default,Priscilla,0,0,0,,那么 就把这个给你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.20,0:01:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.84,0:01:09.36,Default,Priscilla,0,0,0,,你想要这个 而这个又在妾身手里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.36,0:01:12.19,Default,Priscilla,0,0,0,,那么你需要做的事情便只有一件
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.27,0:01:16.25,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,谢了啊普莉茜菈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.25,0:01:17.33,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,太好了 菲鲁特
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.33,0:01:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这么一来说不定就能赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.03,0:01:21.24,Default,Felt,0,0,0,,小哥 你别低头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.24,0:01:24.43,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,这不就是低个头就能解决的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.43,0:01:25.37,Default,Priscilla,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.37,0:01:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,妾身都还没说到舔脚的份上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.51,0:01:31.17,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,你居然想说舔脚啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.17,0:01:32.71,Default,Priscilla,0,0,0,,所以 怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.71,0:01:34.03,Default,Felt,0,0,0,,我不会低头的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.03,0:01:35.02,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,菲鲁特
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.02,0:01:37.98,Default,Felt,0,0,0,,或许低头了就能拿到人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.98,0:01:42.09,Default,Felt,0,0,0,,但这场比试说到底是我和莱茵哈鲁特的比试
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.09,0:01:45.07,Default,Felt,0,0,0,,通过别人把东西让给我来获胜这种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.07,0:01:48.25,Default,Felt,0,0,0,,虽然没办法很好地表达 我总觉得这是不对的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.25,0:01:49.02,Default,Priscilla,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.02,0:01:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是你那渺小的矜持占了上风吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.54,0:01:54.35,Default,Felt,0,0,0,,是的 这就是我渺小的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.35,0:01:58.37,Default,Felt,0,0,0,,但是 如果丢弃了它 感觉我就不再是我自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.37,0:02:01.49,Default,Priscilla,0,0,0,,嗯 这也是一种活法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.49,0:02:05.30,Default,Priscilla,0,0,0,,那么就让妾身见识见识你挣扎的姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.30,0:02:08.03,Default,Felt,0,0,0,,看到了挣扎的我你可别被吓到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.03,0:02:11.87,Default,Priscilla,0,0,0,,那就尽情让妾身惊诧来取悦妾身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.87,0:02:13.65,Default,Felt,0,0,0,,也谢谢小哥你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:16.50,Default,Felt,0,0,0,,我会用这枚硬币一决胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.66,0:02:18.48,Default,Felt,0,0,0,,哦 一决胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.48,0:02:20.55,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,普莉茜菈 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.18,0:02:23.66,Default,Felt,0,0,0,,{\an8}我能做到的 我要夹到一个人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.66,0:02:23.66,Default,Priscilla,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yes, I got one! I got a doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.55,0:02:22.82,Default,Priscilla,0,0,0,,起身并没有做什么值得被感谢的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.82,0:02:24.29,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.66,0:02:25.62,Default,Felt,0,0,0,,{\an8}来吧人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.62,0:02:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Come on! Gimme!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.29,0:02:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.62,0:02:27.97,Default,Felt,0,0,0,,人偶堵住了出不来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.97,0:02:30.42,Default,Priscilla,0,0,0,,尽情挣扎吧 尽情挣扎吧
